{"tid":1789731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"學界張崑陽：立即搞集會講香港金融中心地位受損，將星火議題帶上國際舞台","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T14:22:59.000Z","uid":30209,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"0c300135284de9a6f9785fc129b2e80e79efcb9c","tid":1789731,"uid":30209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"各位手足：<br />\n收到美國國會方面嘅消息，佢哋已經有人留意到匯豐之前取消咗星火個戶口，然後香港警察今日又巧合地凍結咗星火七千萬資產。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會有人係考慮緊用《國際緊急經濟權力法》制裁匯豐，所以大家一定要將呢件事變成國際新聞。香港作為國際金融中心，資本帳一定係自由流動，今日可以巧立名目凍結星火，聽日一定可以控制外資。全球嘅經濟利益就會因為中國嘅政治命令而隨時受損，所以大家唔好掉以輕心真係盡全力搞大佢，例如用Twitter 瘋狂洗版同埋係中環搞一個集會話反對資本控制同國際講香港金融中心地位正在受損。拜托🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJWKM8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJWKM8P.png&h=e71a2ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">星火無條件幫手足咁耐，係時候幫返星火</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1b328bfa654d74eefa36f0266de9c738250053","tid":1789731,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:17:59.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"054b726b689d394345007012019491199af222f2","tid":1789731,"uid":30209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!"},{"pid":"c6941de7476a765df327b284b3f88b1195445532","tid":1789731,"uid":266274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img